WEBVTT

00:00:01.440 --> 00:00:05.136
2014, July 5,

00:00:05.160 --> 00:00:09.360
the Ukrainian army entered
Sloviansk city in eastern Ukraine.

00:00:09.880 --> 00:00:13.816
They gathered all the locals
in Lenin Square.

00:00:13.840 --> 00:00:18.056
Then, they organized
the public crucifixion

00:00:18.080 --> 00:00:21.256
of the son of a pro-Russia militant.

00:00:21.280 --> 00:00:23.760
He was only three years old.

00:00:24.440 --> 00:00:30.936
Refugee Galina Pyshnyak told this story
to Russia's First TV channel.